WIDGET REST API

Built with:
	Java 8, Spring Boot

Documentation of the api can be found as a swagger file which is published by the application under "/swagger.yml" path

To run the application with default port(8080):
	> mvn spring-boot:run 

To run with a different port:
	> mvn spring-boot:run  -Dspring-boot.run.arguments=--server.port=9090
	
To run the application in H2 mode change "h2.enabled" property to true
	> mvn spring-boot:run -Dspring-boot.run.arguments=--h2.enabled=true

To run all integration and unit tests:
	> mvn test
